OL,5, ITV has said it investigated rumours of
OL,6, a relationship between Phillip         
OL,7, Schofield and a younger employee in    
OL,8, 2020 - but both "repeatedly denied" it.
OL,10,FSchofield quit ITV on Friday after     
OL,11,Fadmitting he had had an affair with a  
OL,12,Fyounger male colleague at the network  
OL,13,Fand had lied to cover it up.           
OL,15,FThe TV presenter said the relationship 
OL,16,Fhad been "unwise, but not illegal".    
OL,18,FSome former ITV daytime figures said   
OL,19,Fthe revelations raised questions about 
OL,20,Fhow much the network's managers knew.  
